{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775835737542,"sessionID":"ses_287f3c6b0ffeDZ0hfYvo2PU9oI","part":{"id":"prt_d780c4c05001a1IHSdZZ2QCbKB","messageID":"msg_d780c3a44001vFAwMj5F5rWNH5","sessionID":"ses_287f3c6b0ffeDZ0hfYvo2PU9oI","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_acdd839c4fe14862b4669815","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project at /home/dsj/benchmark thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure (top-level directories and key files)\n2. The pkg/store directory contents (if it exists) - this is where Redis storage implementation should be\n3. Any client-go related code (look for client-go directories, generated Kubernetes client code)\n4. Any test files related to store or client-go\n5. The deployment/client-go.md spec file (if it exists)\n6. Look for any AR-013 related files or references\n\nSearch for:\n- All Go files in pkg/store/\n- All files matching *client* or *runtime* patterns\n- Any Redis-related code\n- Test files for store/client-go\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of what exists in the project, including file paths and their purposes.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_287f3a28dffeAYqSSrBk6BxiyW (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is a comprehensive summary of the AgentCube project at `/home/dsj/benchmark`.\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Project Summary\n\n### 1. Overall Project Structure\n\nThe benchmark root at `/home/dsj/benchmark` is a **benchmarking framework** that evaluates AI coding agents. The actual AgentCube project lives inside a workspace:\n\n**Workspace path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/`\n\n**Top-level directories and key files in the workspace:**\n\n| Path | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `pkg/` | Go source code (APIs, store, router, workloadmanager, common types) |\n| `client-go/` | Generated Kubernetes client code (clientset, informers, listers) |\n| `changes/` | Change requests (AR-004 through AR-013), each with proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md |\n| `deployment/` | Deployment specs including `client-go.md`, `design.md`, `spec.md` |\n| `session-store/` | Session store spec and design documents |\n| `session-routing/` | Session routing spec and design |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/` | Sandbox orchestration spec and design |\n| `ci-cd/` | CI/CD design and spec |\n| `code-execution/` | Code execution spec and design |\n| `integrations/` | Integration spec and design |\n| `idle-cleanup/` | Idle cleanup design and spec |\n| `python-sdk/` | Python SDK design and spec |\n| `cli-toolkit/` | CLI toolkit design and spec |\n| `testing/` | TDD manifest |\n| `go.mod` | Module: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`, Go 1.25.0 |\n| `go.sum` | Dependency checksums |\n| `project.md` | Project context document |\n| `proposal.md` | Top-level proposal |\n| `design.md` | Top-level design |\n| `delta-spec.md` | AR-013 delta spec for Redis store |\n| `test_spec.md` | Test specification |\n| `coverage.out` | Go test coverage output |\n\n---\n\n### 2. pkg/store Directory Contents\n\n**Location:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/store/`\n\n| File | Lines | Purpose |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| `store.go` | 35 | **Store interface** definition with methods: `StoreSandbox`, `UpdateSandbox`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID`, `GetSandbox`, `ListSandboxes`, `UpdateSessionLastActivity`, `ListExpiredSandboxes`, `ListInactiveSandboxes`, `Ping`, `Close`. Also defines `ErrNotFound` sentinel and `Storage()` singleton accessor. |\n| `singleton.go` | 39 | **Provider selection** via `STORE_TYPE` env var (defaults to `redis`, supports `valkey`). Uses `sync.Once` for thread-safe initialization. |\n| `store_redis.go` | 274 | **Redis backend** implementation using `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`. Uses String keys (`session:{id}`) + Sorted Sets (`session:expiry`, `session:last_activity`) for GC indexing. Pipeline-based atomic operations. |\n| `store_valkey.go` | 253 | **Valkey backend** implementation using `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`. Same data model as Redis but uses Valkey's typed command builder API. |\n| `codec.go` | 19 | **JSON encode/decode** helpers for `SandboxInfo` serialization. |\n| `store_redis_test.go` | ~530 | Redis unit tests using `miniredis` (in-memory Redis emulator). Covers all CRUD, list, expiry, orphan handling, constructor validation. |\n| `store_valkey_test.go` | ~236 | Valkey unit tests covering nil handling, zero expiry, constructor validation, interface compliance. |\n| `singleton_test.go` | (exists) | Singleton initialization tests. |\n| `codec_test.go` | (exists) | Codec encode/decode tests. |\n\n**Key Redis data model:**\n- String keys: `session:{sessionID}` -> JSON(SandboxInfo)\n- Sorted Set: `session:expiry` -> {sessionID: ExpiresAt.Unix()}\n- Sorted Set: `session:last_activity` -> {sessionID: lastActivityAt.Unix()}\n\n---\n\n### 3. client-go Related Code\n\n**Location:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/`\n\nThis is a **hand-crafted Kubernetes client** (not code-generator output) for the API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`.\n\n#### clientset/ (9 Go files)\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `clientset/clientset.go` | `Interface` with `RuntimeV1alpha1()` accessor (9 lines) |\n| `clientset/fake.go` | `FakeClientset` with in-memory `ObjectStore` for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter (44 lines) |\n| `clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | **Core implementation**: `ObjectStore` (thread-safe in-memory store), `AgentRuntimeClient`, `CodeInterpreterClient` with full CRUD (Create, Update, UpdateStatus, Delete, Get, List, Watch, Patch) (248 lines) |\n| `clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/client.go` | `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` factory, GVR definitions for agentruntimes and codeinterpreters (39 lines) |\n| `clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/interfaces.go` | Interface definitions: `AgentRuntimeInterface`, `CodeInterpreterInterface`, `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (37 lines) |\n\n#### informers/externalversions/ (3 Go files)\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `factory.go` | `SharedInformerFactory` interface and implementation; supports both fake and real informer factories (65 lines) |\n| `runtime/interface.go` | Group-level interface with `V1alpha1()` accessor (19 lines) |\n| `runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | Version-level interface with `AgentRuntimes()` and `CodeInterpreters()` informers; includes `AgentRuntimeInformer` and `CodeInterpreterInformer` with lazy-initialized `cache.SharedIndexInformer` (86 lines) |\n\n#### listers/runtime/v1alpha1/ (1 Go file)\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `expansion_generated.go` | `AgentRuntimeLister`, `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister`, `CodeInterpreterLister`, `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` with full implementations using `cache.ListAll` and `cache.ListAllByNamespace` (121 lines) |\n\n**API Types managed by client-go:**\n- `AgentRuntime` (CRD: `agentruntimes`) - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go`\n- `CodeInterpreter` (CRD: `codeinterpreters`) - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n\n---\n\n### 4. Test Files Related to store and client-go\n\n**Store test files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/store/store_redis_test.go` - ~30+ test functions covering Ping, GetSandbox, StoreSandbox, UpdateSandbox, DeleteSandboxBySessionID, ListSandboxes, ListExpiredSandboxes, ListInactiveSandboxes, UpdateSessionLastActivity, Close, constructor validation, orphan handling\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/store/store_valkey_test.go` - ~15+ test functions covering nil handling, zero expiry, constructor validation, interface compliance\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/store/singleton_test.go` - Singleton initialization tests\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/store/codec_test.go` - JSON codec tests\n\n**Other test files in the project (19 total):**\n- `pkg/router/middleware_test.go`, `jwt_test.go`, `server_test.go`, `config_test.go`\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/metrics_test.go`\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go`\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go`, `sandbox_delete_test.go`\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info_test.go`, `codeinterpreter_types_test.go`, `constants_test.go`, `shared_types_test.go`, `agent_type_test.go`\n\n**Note:** There are **no test files in the client-go/ directory**. The client-go code is tested indirectly through the workloadmanager/handler tests that use `FakeClientset`.\n\n---\n\n### 5. deployment/client-go.md Spec File\n\n**Exists in two locations:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/client-go.md` (spec reference)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/client-go.md` (workspace copy, identical content)\n\n**Content:** 241-line specification describing the generated Kubernetes client code for API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`. Covers:\n- Clientset Interface and constructors\n- Typed clients for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n- SharedInformerFactory\n- Listers (AgentRuntimeLister, CodeInterpreterLister)\n- Fake clients\n- Complete file index of all client-go files\n- Regeneration command: `make gen-client` -> `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n\n---\n\n### 6. AR-013 Related Files and References\n\n**AR-013 = \"Redis Storage Implementation\"** for `pkg/store` module.\n\n**AR-013 files in the workspace:**\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-013/proposal.md` | Problem statement, proposed solution, scope (in/out), dependencies, risks (90 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-013/design.md` | Full architecture design with Redis data model, interface specifications, method specs, error handling matrix, testing strategy, deployment considerations (707 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md` | 9 tasks (T1-T9) with detailed subtasks, dependencies, acceptance criteria (150 lines) |\n\n**AR-013 log files (benchmark execution logs):**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-013_ST-0.log` through `AR-013_ST-4.log`\n\n**AR-013 delta spec:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` - 244-line Gherkin-style spec with scenarios for all Redis store operations\n\n**Related change requests in the same project:**\n- AR-004, AR-005, AR-006, AR-008, AR-009, AR-010, AR-011, AR-012 (each with proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md)\n\n---\n\n### 7. Redis-Related Code Summary\n\nRedis code is found exclusively in `pkg/store/`:\n\n| File | Redis Library | Key Features |\n|------|--------------|--------------|\n| `store_redis.go` | `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` v9.18.0 | Pipeline-based atomic ops, ZSET indexing, env-based config |\n| `store_valkey.go` | `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` v1.0.73 | Typed command builder API, cluster support options |\n| `store_redis_test.go` | `github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2` v2.37.0 | In-memory Redis for testing |\n\nBoth implementations share the same `Store` interface and data model, selected at runtime via `STORE_TYPE` environment variable.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_287f3a28dffeAYqSSrBk6BxiyW","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775835569520,"end":1775835737539}}}}
