{"type":"text","timestamp":1775835943556,"sessionID":"ses_287f3c6b0ffeDZ0hfYvo2PU9oI","part":{"id":"prt_d78118bf8001jSbbCtD4nMidvL","messageID":"msg_d78118591001Xj54MnMDtk3GVL","sessionID":"ses_287f3c6b0ffeDZ0hfYvo2PU9oI","type":"text","text":"## AR-013 Verification Report\n\n### Overall: **FAIL** — Multiple spec deviations and 5 failing tests\n\n---\n\n### A. AR-013 (Redis Storage) — pkg/store\n\n#### Acceptance Criteria Status\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Detail |\n|---|-----------|--------|--------|\n| AC1 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` | **PASS** | Compiles cleanly |\n| AC2 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -v` | **FAIL** | 5 of 53 tests fail |\n| AC3 | `go test -race ./pkg/store/...` | **FAIL** | Same 5 failures, no races |\n| AC4 | Coverage >= 80% | **FAIL** | 57.4% |\n| AC5 | `go vet ./pkg/store/...` | **PASS** | No warnings |\n| AC6 | Interface matches design.md S3.1 | **FAIL** | 4 signature mismatches |\n| AC7 | `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs` uses MGet | **PASS** (Redis only) | Valkey still uses loop GET |\n| AC8 | `StoreSandbox` rejects zero ExpiresAt | **PASS** | Both Redis and Valkey |\n| AC9 | Constructor returns error | **PASS** | But missing ping validation |\n\n#### Spec Deviations (AR-013)\n\n| # | Requirement | Expected | Actual | Severity |\n|---|-------------|----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | `ErrNotFound` message | `\"store: not found\"` | `\"sandbox not found\"` (store.go:12) | **HIGH** |\n| 2 | `GetSandbox` renamed | `GetSandboxBySessionID` | Still `GetSandbox` (store.go:18) | **HIGH** |\n| 3 | `StoreSandbox` signature | `(ctx, *SandboxInfo)` | `(ctx, sessionID string, *SandboxInfo)` (store.go:15) | **HIGH** |\n| 4 | `UpdateSandbox` signature | `(ctx, *SandboxInfo)` | `(ctx, sessionID string, *SandboxInfo)` (store.go:16) | **HIGH** |\n| 5 | `limit` parameter type | `int64` | `int` (store.go:22-23) | **MEDIUM** |\n| 6 | `cli` field type | `*redis.Client` | `redis.UniversalClient` (store_redis.go:17) | **LOW** |\n| 7 | Constructor ping | `cli.Ping()` validates connection | No ping in `newRedisStore()` (store_redis.go:40-47) | **MEDIUM** |\n| 8 | Valkey List uses MGET | `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs` | Loop GET (store_valkey.go:206-215, 232-241) | **MEDIUM** |\n| 9 | Valkey `limit` type | `int64` | `int` (store_valkey.go:194, 220) | **MEDIUM** |\n| 10 | No `log.Printf` | Confirmed | None found | PASS |\n\n#### Failing Tests (5)\n\n| Test | Root Cause |\n|------|------------|\n| `TestRedisStore_DeleteSandboxBySessionID` (line 181) | `mr.ZMembers()` errors on deleted ZSET; test should handle missing key |\n| `TestRedisStore_UpdateSessionLastActivity_EmptySessionID` (line 238) | Test expects `\"sessionID cannot be empty\"` but impl returns `\"sessionID is empty\"` |\n| `TestRedisStore_ListInactiveSandboxes` (line 382) | Both sandboxes have `LastActivityAt` in the past relative to `time.Now()`, so both match — test logic flaw |\n| `TestValkeyStore_ListExpiredSandboxes_ScoreCalculation` (line 213) | Test expects negative score `-3600` but impl stores absolute Unix timestamp |\n| `TestValkeyStore_ListInactiveSandboxes_ScoreCalculation` (line 220) | Same as above — expects `-7200`, gets absolute Unix timestamp |\n\n---\n\n### B. client-go — deployment/client-go.md Spec\n\n#### File Index Compliance\n\n| Spec File | Exists | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | **Partial** | Missing `Discovery()`, no `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` embed, missing 4 constructors |\n| `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go` | **MISSING** | No scheme/codecs package |\n| `clientset/versioned/scheme/doc.go` | **MISSING** | |\n| `clientset/versioned/fake/clientset_generated.go` | **Partial** | Exists as `clientset/fake.go` but different structure |\n| `clientset/versioned/fake/register.go` | **MISSING** | |\n| `clientset/versioned/fake/doc.go` | **MISSING** | |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | **Partial** | No `RESTClient()` method, no `rest.Interface` usage |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | **MISSING** | Methods inlined in `runtime_client.go` |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | **MISSING** | Methods inlined in `runtime_client.go` |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/generated_expansion.go` | **MISSING** | No expansion interfaces |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | **MISSING** | |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/*` (4 files) | **MISSING** | |\n| `informers/externalversions/factory.go` | **Partial** | Missing `ForResource`, `InformerFor`, `internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory` |\n| `informers/externalversions/generic.go` | **MISSING** | |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` | **Partial** | Exists but simplified |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | **Partial** | Missing `New(factory, namespace, tweakListOptions)` |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | **MISSING** | Inlined in `interface.go` |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | **MISSING** | Inlined in `interface.go` |\n| `informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go` | **MISSING** | |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | **Partial** | Inlined in `expansion_generated.go`, missing expansion |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | **Partial** | Inlined in `expansion_generated.go`, missing expansion |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` | **Partial** | Missing expansion interfaces |\n\n**21 spec files expected, 9 exist (all partial), 12 missing.**\n\n#### Interface Gaps\n\n| Spec Interface | Missing Members |\n|----------------|-----------------|\n| `clientset.Interface` | `Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface` |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` | `RESTClient() rest.Interface` |\n| `AgentRuntimeInterface` | `DeleteCollection()`, `AgentRuntimeExpansion` embedding |\n| `CodeInterpreterInterface` | `DeleteCollection()`, `CodeInterpreterExpansion` embedding |\n| `SharedInformerFactory` | `ForResource()`, `InformerFor()`, `WaitForCacheSync` returns `map[string]bool` not `map[reflect.Type]bool` |\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n**AR-013 (pkg/store)**: ~60% compliant. Core Redis data model and pipeline operations are correct. The 4 interface signature changes from the proposal were never applied. 5 test failures (3 test bugs, 2 impl/test mismatch). Coverage at 57.4% is below the 80% gate.\n\n**client-go**: ~40% compliant. Hand-crafted simplified implementation covers basic CRUD via in-memory store but is missing the full generated client structure: no `discovery`, no `rest.Interface`-based REST client, no scheme registration, no fake typed clients, no generic informer routing, and 12 of 21 spec files are absent.","time":{"start":1775835943553,"end":1775835943553}}}
